headline: Zimmer Biomet Completes Acquisition of Paragon 28
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. ("Zimmer Biomet"; NYSE and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today announced it has completed the acquisition of Paragon 28, Inc. ("Paragon 28"), a leading medical device company focused exclusively on the fast-growing foot and ankle orthopedic space.
